ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
PrecisApprove that GREG ARASON of Winnipeg, Manitoba, continue to act as Interim President of The Canadian Wheat Board for a term exceeding ninety days, until such time as a new President is appointed, effective March 19, 2007.
